email

write an email -->
    me@163.com to friend@gmail.com
use a email software -->
    Mail User Agent 邮箱用户代理(MUA)
transfer to 163-->
    Mail Transfer Agent (MTA)
163 to gmail -->
    MTA to MTA
gmail to MDA-->
    Mail Delivery Agent 邮箱投递代理
    friend open email with her MUA

code----
    1. 编写 MUA发邮件到MTA
    2. 编写 MUA从MDA上收邮件

protocol
    send email:
        SMTP : Simple Mail Transfer Protocol
    receive email:
        POP3 : Post Office Protocol 3
        IMAP4 : Internet Message Access Protocol 4
